                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17991030-46-off259 t17991030-46-cd260"></join>, two iron bars, 21lb. weight, value 5s. the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t17991030-46-victim456" type="victimName">
                           Thomas 
                           Poynder
                        <interp inst="t17991030-46-victim456" type="surname" value="Poynder"></interp>
